Gross bookings increased by 4.0% for the year ended December 31, 2019, compared to the year ended December 31, 2018
(growth on a constant-currency basis was approximately 8%), almost entirely due to growth of 11.2% in accommodation
44
room night reservations, partially offset by the negative impact of foreign currency exchange rate fluctuations and a 2% decrease in
