international businesses for the year ended December 31, 2019 increased by 4.1%, compared to the year ended December 31, 2018
(growth on a constant-currency basis was approximately 8%). Total revenues attributable to our U.S. businesses were relatively flat
for the year ended December 31, 2019 compared to the year ended December 31, 2018.
