17. BENEFIT PLANS
 
The Company maintains a defined contribution 401(k) savings plan (the "Plan") covering certain U.S. employees. In
connection with acquisitions, effective at the date of such acquisitions, the Company assumed defined contribution plans covering
the U.S. employees of the acquired companies. The Company also maintains certain other defined contribution plans outside of the
United States for which it provides contributions for participating employees.  The Company's matching contributions during the
years ended December 31, 2019, 2018 and 2017 were $26 million, $22 million and $15 million, respectively.
